cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO 

This paper focuses on computer vision tasks related to rendered images, specifically semantic segmentation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with 3D scenes, which suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.GR (Graphics). The use of data-driven approaches and algorithms for view selection suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the mention of a search algorithm suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.RO (Robotics and Control).
